title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter should display in data set dialog.
description: The output parameter is not being displayed in the data set dialog.
OB: Currently, when calling a stored procedure from the Oracle database, the query result stored in the output parameter is not visible in the data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Call a stored procedure from the Oracle database.
2. Check the data set dialog to see if the output parameter is displayed.
